title: Using a CSV
body: Tik Tok has the ability to use CSV, comma (or any other) separated values, file. You can check look at the CSV file for this example directly.

title: Separate file
body: CSV's are separate files from the page so we need a way to get their data on the page for Tik Tok to use. In this example, we are using jQuery to do that.

title: CSV options
body: As your CSV could actually have any delimiter such as a pipe (|), there are a couple options to handle this. csvDelimiter will change which character separates a field; the default is a comma (,). And csvQuote which tells Tik Tok which character wraps a field; the default is the double quote (").
